    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in wonderful shape, ready for all your upcoming road trips! It drives super smoothly and has been really well-maintained over the years. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
