    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a peaky power band that thrives near its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This chassis has been proactively maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing precision. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior displays honest wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and suspension kinematics\u2014remain sharp and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 31000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
